title: Crossed - Badlands Patient Zero Ashcan (2013) (c2c) (DarkNahga-E
description: C-Day is just around the corner and GARTH ENNIS has a little holiday present for you! It's an exclusive sneak peek ashcan for his new Crossed: Badlands #50 arc "Patient Zero." That's right, Garth is finally visiting the first breakout of the virus and it could mean that some of the biggest questions finally get answered! Also included is a special Jacen Burrows advance-look cover gallery. Get ready for the most eagerly anticipated Crossed story ever and you can have a front row seat for the insanity with this special preview limited to just 5000 copies!
